Individual




Robert Loughran



Mr. Robert Loughran, CPA, is Chief Accounting Officer & Vice President at Avon Products, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Avon Cosmetics Ltd. Mr. Loughran was previously employed as Senior Director by Gartner, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Connecticut.



